OL,3,CTwo men accused of child sex abuse
OL,4,Cplead not guilty to 27 further charges
OL,6,FTwo men accused of sexually abusing
OL,7,Fchildren at a former children's
OL,8,Fassessment centre in Monmouthshire
OL,9,Fhave pleaded not guilty to a further
OL,10,F27 charges against them.
OL,12,FAngus Riddell denied 22 new charges,
OL,13,Fincluding rape, indecent assault,
OL,14,Findecency with a child and child
OL,15,Fcruelty.
OL,17,FThe offences are alleged to have
OL,18,Fhappened between the 1970s and 1990s.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
