PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1782771508
OL,3,CTwo men accused of child sex abuse
OL,4,Cplead not guilty to 27 further charges
OL,6,FRobin Griffiths denied five fresh
OL,7,Fallegations - said to have taken place
OL,8,Fin the 1980s and 90s - including
OL,9,Findecent assault and indecency with a
OL,10,Fchild.
OL,12,FThe pair previously pleaded not guilty
OL,13,Fto 45 separate charges between them.
OL,15,FThe allegations relate to the Coed
OL,16,FGlas Assessment Centre in Abergavenny,
OL,17,Fwhich opened in 1977 before closing in
OL,18,F1995.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
