PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1782771508
OL,3,CTwo men accused of child sex abuse
OL,4,Cplead not guilty to 27 further charges
OL,6,FNewport Crown Court heard that Mr
OL,7,FRiddell started working at Coed Glas
OL,8,Fin 1979. Mr Griffiths joined the
OL,9,Ffollowing year.
OL,11,FTwo other defendants have pleaded not
OL,12,Fguilty to child cruelty charges.
OL,14,FLisa Gething, who worked in a number
OL,15,Fof different roles at the centre from
OL,16,Fthe mid 1980s, denies nine counts of
OL,17,Fchild cruelty.
OL,19,FSimon Bevan, who worked at Coed Glas
OL,20,Fin the early 1990s, denies two counts
OL,21,Fof the same offence.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
