PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1782771508
OL,3,CTwo men accused of child sex abuse
OL,4,Cplead not guilty to 27 further charges
OL,6,FIn total, the four defendants face 83
OL,7,Fcharges between them.
OL,9,FJudge Daniel Williams said they would
OL,10,Fface trial together, with a trial date
OL,11,Fset for 18 January next year at
OL,12,FNewport Crown Court.
OL,14,FIt comes amid an ongoing police
OL,15,Finvestigation into allegations of
OL,16,Fphysical and sexual abuse at the
OL,17,Fcentre, codenamed Operation Spinney.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
