OL,3,CTwo men accused of child sex abuse
OL,4,Cplead not guilty to 27 further charges
OL,6,F"We take all reports of child abuse
OL,7,Fseriously and would urge anyone who
OL,8,Fhas suffered abuse or has concerns
OL,9,Fabout someone who may be suffering to
OL,10,Fcome forward and speak to the police.
OL,12,F"We will listen to you and investigate
OL,13,Fall offences and also ensure you have
OL,14,Faccess to any help or support you
OL,15,Fneed."
